column3: What's your name? Make sure to enter your name the same way every single time.
column4: Which video are you giving feedback for? Copy-paste the .mp4 file. So if the file is named "video_name.mp4", put "video_name" here.
column6: Give feedback. Again, be natural! Speak the way you'd want to speak to your personal robot assistant. Even if the task isn't inherently interesting, feel free to be creative - ask to change the order, the location, and more.
Slow it down and put it in the other bin.
